28
00:03:12,590 --> 00:03:13,720
Drink some tea then.

29
00:03:14,080 --> 00:03:14,750
Thank you.

30
00:03:27,590 --> 00:03:28,990
The liquor tastes great.

31
00:03:29,600 --> 00:03:30,880
Li likes drinking too.

32
00:03:30,910 --> 00:03:31,560
He didn't join us today.

33
00:03:31,560 --> 00:03:32,280
What a pity.

34
00:03:33,000 --> 00:03:34,800
He took a leave and went back to his hometown.

35
00:03:34,800 --> 00:03:35,280
A leave?

36
00:03:35,400 --> 00:03:36,000
Why?

37
00:03:37,850 --> 00:03:39,000
