54
00:04:03,310 --> 00:04:04,250
Seriously?

55
00:04:04,400 --> 00:04:05,430
You've never been married.

56
00:04:05,430 --> 00:04:06,470
Of course I have.

57
00:04:19,360 --> 00:04:20,490
That was just a joke.

58
00:04:21,240 --> 00:04:22,640
I've never been married.

59
00:04:39,920 --> 00:04:40,980
Careful. Careful.

60
00:04:47,400 --> 00:04:48,460
I'm telling you...

61
00:04:48,510 --> 00:04:49,570
Watch your tongue.

62
00:04:49,950 --> 00:04:50,810
Physician Jiu.

63
00:04:52,190 --> 00:04:53,240
Mr. Yan?

64
00:04:56,390 --> 00:04:57,390
You can leave now.

65
00:04:57,510 --> 00:04:58,710
No need to wait for me.

66
00:05:01,360 --> 00:05:01,890
Let's go.

67
00:05:03,070 --> 00:05:04,600
Shall I wait for you downstairs?

68
00:05:04,600 --> 00:05:05,510
No, I'm all good.

69
00:05:05,510 --> 00:05:06,710
You should get going.

70
00:05:06,870 --> 00:05:07,470
Tingzhou,

71
00:05:07,600 --> 00:05:08,600
take Banxia home.

72
00:05:09,360 --> 00:05:09,720
Okay.

73
00:05:10,120 --> 00:05:10,580
Chi Xue.

74
00:05:16,340 --> 00:05:17,480
[Yanlai Restaurant]

75
00:05:16,920 --> 00:05:18,120
Slow down. Slow down.

76
00:05:18,400 --> 00:05:20,190
You gotta be careful these days.

77
00:05:20,190 --> 00:05:20,800
Banxia?

78
00:05:21,950 --> 00:05:23,210
Didn't I tell you to go?

79
00:05:23,430 --> 00:05:24,830
Why are you waiting here?

80
00:05:25,040 --> 00:05:25,720
I don't have much

81
00:05:25,720 --> 00:05:26,850
