92
00:05:55,310 --> 00:05:55,840
Let's go.

93
00:05:57,950 --> 00:05:58,800
Come with me.

94
00:06:14,750 --> 00:06:15,410
Here we are.

95
00:06:22,160 --> 00:06:23,190
Get some rest.

96
00:06:23,680 --> 00:06:25,540
I'll come to see you off tomorrow.

97
00:06:25,920 --> 00:06:26,380
No need.

98
00:06:28,890 --> 00:06:30,090
You're confused now.

99
00:06:30,430 --> 00:06:31,800
Before you get your head

100
00:06:32,110 --> 00:06:32,800
straight,

101
00:06:33,409 --> 00:06:34,290
it's unnecessary for us

102
00:06:34,290 --> 00:06:35,090
to meet again.

103
00:06:37,600 --> 00:06:38,530
What do you mean?

104
00:06:40,430 --> 00:06:41,190
I don't know what

105
00:06:41,190 --> 00:06:42,390
is making you do this.

106
00:06:42,630 --> 00:06:43,870
But when you think it through,

107
00:06:43,870 --> 00:06:45,360
you can come to the capital city for me.

108
00:06:45,360 --> 00:06:47,360
You'll have one year to mull it over.

109
00:06:49,480 --> 00:06:50,280
Chu Youhuang,

110
00:06:51,220 --> 00:06:52,680
you're not my only choice.

111
00:07:06,480 --> 00:07:07,080
Thank you.

112
00:07:07,990 --> 00:07:08,630
Enjoy.

113
00:07:14,920 --> 00:07:15,410
So delicious.

114
00:07:15,410 --> 00:07:16,050
Get a bite.

115
00:07:17,830 --> 00:07:19,380
If you want me to eat it,

116
00:07:19,560 --> 00:07:21,690
why didn't you just buy two bowls of it?

117
00:07:23,240 --> 00:07:25,170
One is enough for both of us.

118
00:07:29,860 --> 00:07:31,060
You're not eating it.

119
00:07:31,120 --> 00:07:32,320
Do you hate me or what?

120
00:07:33,000 --> 00:07:33,830
No, I don't.

121
00:07:34,870 --> 00:07:35,330
Come on,

122
00:07:35,510 --> 00:07:36,190
try some.

123
00:07:44,600 --> 00:07:45,730
It's good, isn't it?

124
00:07:46,290 --> 00:07:46,880
Yes.

125
00:07:49,870 --> 00:07:50,470
You eat it.

126
00:07:50,680 --> 00:07:51,680
It's all yours.

127
00:08:02,680 --> 00:08:04,010
It's quite late now.

128
00:08:04,210 --> 00:08:06,740
I'll take you home after you finish this bowl.

129
00:08:06,790 --> 00:08:08,260
So soon?

130
00:08:08,750 --> 00:08:10,680
I'm not done wandering around yet.

131
00:08:11,750 --> 00:08:12,660
You don't want

132
00:08:13,030 --> 00:08:15,030
your parents to get worried, do you?

133
00:08:15,210 --> 00:08:16,000
I already told them

134
00:08:16,000 --> 00:08:17,360
this would take a while when I left.

135
00:08:17,360 --> 00:08:18,760
Don't you worry about it.

136
00:08:22,070 --> 00:08:23,680
How are they doing lately?

137
00:08:24,310 --> 00:08:26,320
Is the medicine working?

138
00:08:27,630 --> 00:08:29,310
My father is much better now.

139
00:08:29,750 --> 00:08:30,750
But my mother

140
00:08:31,590 --> 00:08:32,990
still doesn't feel well.

141
00:08:33,360 --> 00:08:35,159
She's having dreams very often,

142
00:08:35,390 --> 00:08:38,049
and can't sleep without the calming fragrance.

143
00:08:38,480 --> 00:08:39,390
But the frequent use of it

144
00:08:39,390 --> 00:08:40,590
is harmful to health.

145
00:08:42,390 --> 00:08:42,960
Well,

146
00:08:43,360 --> 00:08:44,320
I'll make a

147
00:08:44,440 --> 00:08:45,150
nerve-soothing

148
00:08:45,150 --> 00:08:46,440
and sleep-aiding prescription

149
00:08:46,440 --> 00:08:47,570
for you to take home.

150
00:08:48,840 --> 00:08:49,320
Okay.

151
00:08:56,760 --> 00:08:58,000
Do you remember

152
00:08:58,030 --> 00:08:59,270
the wish we made here?

153
00:08:59,910 --> 00:09:02,000
Now it has come true.

154
00:09:02,550 --> 00:09:04,410
My parents have come back safely.

155
00:09:07,870 --> 00:09:09,330
However, for some reason,

156
00:09:10,720 --> 00:09:12,790
my mother doesn't seem to like me.

157
00:09:14,270 --> 00:09:15,750
She always avoids me.

158
00:09:16,670 --> 00:09:18,600
She speaks too politely to me.

159
00:09:19,240 --> 00:09:20,910
She hates it when I touch her.

160
00:09:22,690 --> 00:09:23,380
Xuanye,

161
00:09:25,000 --> 00:09:25,840
tell me.

162
00:09:26,840 --> 00:09:27,870
Am I not being

163
00:09:27,870 --> 00:09:29,200
a good enough daughter?

164
00:09:31,240 --> 00:09:32,360
I've grown up,

165
00:09:32,510 --> 00:09:33,360
but not in the way

166
00:09:33,360 --> 00:09:34,670
she likes.

167
00:09:34,870 --> 00:09:36,730
Is that why she's acting this way?

168
00:09:37,630 --> 00:09:38,840
You know

169
00:09:39,270 --> 00:09:41,200
what your mother has been through.

170
00:09:41,770 --> 00:09:43,680
She was a Guanyin Bodhisattva statue for over 10 years.

171
00:09:43,680 --> 00:09:45,210
She couldn't speak or move.

172
00:09:45,480 --> 00:09:48,520
Clear though her mind was, she was controlled by others.

173
00:09:48,520 --> 00:09:49,480
Do you know how

174
00:09:49,510 --> 00:09:50,710
despairing that was?

175
00:09:54,670 --> 00:09:55,960
She didn't commit suicide,

176
00:09:55,960 --> 00:09:56,630
go insane,

177
00:09:56,960 --> 00:09:58,560
or become completely different.

178
00:09:58,560 --> 00:09:59,870
It wasn't easy for her.

179
00:10:00,390 --> 00:10:01,360
The effects

180
00:10:01,660 --> 00:10:03,990
of past experiences sometimes linger on.

181
00:10:04,320 --> 00:10:05,520
I've seen many people

182
00:10:06,140 --> 00:10:06,740
who couldn't

183
00:10:06,740 --> 00:10:08,270
reconcile with their past.

184
00:10:09,080 --> 00:10:09,720
Your mother

185
00:10:09,720 --> 00:10:11,120
is doing a good enough job

186
00:10:11,120 --> 00:10:12,080
coming this far.

187
00:10:12,960 --> 00:10:14,220
You should be patient,

188
00:10:14,630 --> 00:10:16,230
and spend more time with her.

189
00:10:17,910 --> 00:10:18,910
You're right.

190
00:10:19,870 --> 00:10:21,870
I was not being considerate enough.

191
00:10:25,550 --> 00:10:26,880
You know so many things.

192
00:10:28,120 --> 00:10:30,180
I do, only when I'm compared with you.

193
00:10:35,150 --> 00:10:36,080
That was scary.

194
00:10:38,190 --> 00:10:39,080
I don't think I can

195
00:10:39,080 --> 00:10:41,010
enjoy fireworks shows these days.

196
00:10:44,320 --> 00:10:46,050
We're already back to reality.

197
00:10:46,520 --> 00:10:47,510
Everything in the painting

198
00:10:47,510 --> 00:10:48,770
was untrue, wasn't it?

199
00:10:49,030 --> 00:10:50,690
But it was still frightening.

200
00:10:51,360 --> 00:10:51,870
Banxia,

201
00:10:53,000 --> 00:10:54,530
have you ever thought about

202
00:10:54,680 --> 00:10:56,210
what your life would be like

203
00:10:56,550 --> 00:10:58,080
if you couldn't see demons?

204
00:11:00,910 --> 00:11:02,700
