205
00:11:04,150 --> 00:11:06,080
My life would be happier.

206
00:11:06,630 --> 00:11:08,390
My father would still be an official,

207
00:11:08,390 --> 00:11:10,250
and my mother wouldn't have left.

208
00:11:11,150 --> 00:11:12,320
We could've been

209
00:11:12,320 --> 00:11:13,520
closer to each other.

210
00:11:15,840 --> 00:11:18,270
