218
00:11:40,030 --> 00:11:40,630
Because

219
00:11:40,630 --> 00:11:42,630
I wouldn't have met you in that case.

220
00:11:50,870 --> 00:11:51,630
Well,

221
00:11:52,200 --> 00:11:53,030
Xuanye,

222
00:11:54,630 --> 00:11:56,080
you said everything in the painting

223
00:11:56,080 --> 00:11:57,060
was untrue.

224
00:11:58,270 --> 00:11:59,460
Does that mean what you said to me

225
00:11:59,460 --> 00:12:00,420
was also untrue?

226
00:12:02,480 --> 00:12:03,610
What did I say to you?

227
00:12:05,150 --> 00:12:06,410
Have you forgotten it?

228
00:12:07,960 --> 00:12:08,870
How could you forget

229
00:12:08,870 --> 00:12:10,320
