236
00:12:18,710 --> 00:12:19,960
There were many stars.

237
00:12:19,960 --> 00:12:21,090
The moon was hidden.

238
00:12:21,510 --> 00:12:22,480
Then, the moment

239
00:12:22,480 --> 00:12:23,860
the fireworks showed up,

240
00:12:23,860 --> 00:12:24,630
you told me

241
00:12:25,030 --> 00:12:26,120
that you liked me.

242
00:12:26,150 --> 00:12:26,630
You said

243
00:12:27,240 --> 00:12:28,000
you had kept

244
