259
00:12:57,030 --> 00:12:57,960
Maybe we should go.

260
00:12:57,960 --> 00:12:58,480
No!

261
00:12:59,080 --> 00:12:59,750
We have to

262
00:12:59,750 --> 00:13:01,150
