265
00:13:06,080 --> 00:13:06,870
Of course.

266
00:13:07,080 --> 00:13:07,870
It's an important issue.

267
00:13:07,870 --> 00:13:09,330
It must be stated clearly.

268
00:13:09,390 --> 00:13:10,790
You can't just

269
00:13:10,900 --> 00:13:12,180
patronize me, right?

270
00:13:12,650 --> 00:13:13,670
You must

271
00:13:13,670 --> 00:13:14,870
